    <abstract id="aspace_4b01228504b029ecd2a4163ba51e1a37">This microfilmed collection contains the records of St. Peters Evangelical (Slovak) Lutheran Church. The records cover the period 1887-1979 and include baptisms, confirmations, communions, marriages, deaths, anniversary booklets, and lists of council members and pastors.</abstract>
